ECMO US

Joshua Geiger

2023-10-29

A total of 817 pateints were identified since January 2013 with a total of 833 ecmo cannulations. The dataset was filtered for patietns > 18 years old who had peripheral VA - ECMO (Femoral cannulation).

Descriptive statistics

There are 523 subjects within the dataset. Of which there were 4 amputations and 23 fasciotomies.
